# Remote Vault
IMAPStore proton-remote
Account proton

# Local Vault
MaildirStore proton-local
Path ~/.mail/proton/
Inbox ~/.mail/proton/INBOX
Subfolders Verbatim

# Sync Channel
Channel proton-default
Far :proton-remote:
Near :proton-local:
Patterns * !"All Mail"
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

# Sync Inbox
Group proton
Channel proton-default
